msgid "Estimation failed"
msgstr "估計失敗"

msgid ""
"Parameter estimates from the mediation model, organized by direct effects, "
"indirect effects, and total effects."
msgstr ""

msgid "Direct effects"
msgstr "直接效果"

msgid ""
"Direct effects of predictors on outcomes, bypassing all mediators (the c or "
"c' path). A significant direct effect indicates that the predictor "
"influences the outcome independently of the mediation pathway."
msgstr ""

msgid "Indirect effects"
msgstr "間接效果"

msgid ""
"Indirect effects of predictors on outcomes transmitted through mediators. "
"Each indirect effect is the product of the path coefficients along the "
"mediation pathway (a × b). A significant indirect effect indicates that "
"mediation occurs through that pathway."
msgstr ""

msgid "Total Effects"
msgstr "總效果"

msgid ""
"Total effects combining the direct effect and all indirect effects for each "
"predictor-outcome pair. The total effect equals the sum of the direct and "
"indirect effects (c = c' + a × b)."
msgstr ""

msgid "Total indirect effects"
msgstr "所有間接效果"

msgid ""
"Total indirect effects summed across all mediators for each predictor-"
"outcome pair. When there are multiple mediators, this gives the combined "
"strength of all indirect pathways."
msgstr ""

msgid "Residual covariances"
msgstr "殘差共變數"

msgid ""
"Estimated residual covariances between endogenous variables (mediators and "
"outcomes). These represent shared variance not accounted for by the model's "
"directed paths."
msgstr ""

msgid "Path coefficients"
msgstr "路徑係數"

msgid ""
"Individual path coefficients in the mediation model. These include the a "
"paths (predictor to mediator) and b paths (mediator to outcome), which "
"constitute the building blocks of indirect effects."
msgstr ""

msgid "Estimator is %s."
msgstr "估計法為 %s。"

msgid ""
"%1$s Not all bootstrap samples were successful: CI based on %2$.0f samples."
msgstr ""
"%1$s 並非所有拔靴法樣本皆分析成功: 信賴區間是基於 %2$.0f 的樣本分析結果。"

msgid ""
"Proportion of variance in each mediator and outcome variable explained by "
"its predictors in the mediation model."
msgstr ""

#, fuzzy
msgid "Path Plot"
msgstr "路徑圖"

msgid ""
"Visual representation of the mediation model showing predictors, mediators, "
"outcomes, directed paths, and (optionally) parameter estimates."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Currently it is not possible to plot mediation models with ordinal "
"variables. The plot could not be generated."
msgstr "因包含次序變數而無法繪製中介模型圖，無法產生圖形。"

msgid ""
"The plot could not be generated. The underlying code resulted in the "
"following error message: %s"
msgstr "無法產生圖形。錯誤訊息後所列之語法有誤: %s"

msgid "Model syntax"
msgstr "模型的 Lavaan 程式碼"

msgid ""
"The lavaan model syntax automatically generated from the mediation analysis "
"specification. This shows the exact model fitted, including labeled direct "
"and indirect effect parameters."
msgstr ""

msgid "FIML only available with ML-type estimators."
msgstr "只有使用最大概似法 (ML)類估計法時才提供完全訊息最大概似法(FIML)功能。"

msgid ""
"Estimation failed! Message: The model did not converge. Try using a "
"different estimator or specify an other MIMIC model."
msgstr "估計失敗！訊息：模型無法收斂。試使用其他估計法，或改用其他MIMIC模型。"

msgid ""
"Chi-square goodness-of-fit test for the MIMIC model. Both the baseline "
"(independence) model and the factor model with predictors are shown. A non-"
"significant chi-square for the factor model indicates adequate fit."
msgstr ""

msgid "&#967;&sup2;"
msgstr "&#967;&sup2;"

msgid "Factor model"
msgstr "因素模型"

msgid ""
"Parameter estimates for the MIMIC (Multiple Indicators, Multiple Causes) "
"model. The model has observed predictors influencing a latent variable, "
"which in turn is measured by observed indicators."
msgstr ""

msgid "Predictor coefficients"
msgstr "預測變數係數"

msgid ""
"Regression coefficients of the observed predictor (cause) variables on the "
"latent variable. These represent the direct effects of each predictor on the "
"latent construct."
msgstr ""

msgid "Indicator coefficients"
msgstr "指標係數"

msgid ""
"Factor loadings of the latent variable on its observed indicators. These "
"represent how strongly each indicator reflects the underlying latent "
"construct."
msgstr ""

msgid "Indicator"
msgstr "指標"

msgid ""
"Proportion of variance explained in the latent variable (by the predictors) "
"and in each indicator (by the latent variable)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Path diagram of the MIMIC model showing observed predictors (causes), the "
"latent variable, and its observed indicators."
msgstr ""

msgid "Model plot not available with ordinal variables"
msgstr "使用次序變數分析時，無法提供模型圖"

msgid ""
"The lavaan model syntax specifying the MIMIC model structure, including the "
"measurement model and the regression of the latent variable on the "
"predictors."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Specify both factor indicator variables and moderator variables to run the "
"analysis."
msgstr "請同時指定因子指標變數與調節變數以執行分析。"

msgid "Check the 'Sync Analysis' box to run the analysis."
msgstr "勾選「同步分析」方塊以執行分析。"

msgid ""
"The moderator variable '%s' already has '_squared' in its name. Please "
