msgid "Weights"
msgstr "加權"

msgid ""
"Outer weights relating observed indicators to their composite constructs. "
"Weights determine how indicators are combined to form construct scores and "
"reflect each indicator's relative contribution."
msgstr ""

msgid "Construct"
msgstr "構念"

msgid ""
"Outer loadings (correlations) between indicators and their constructs. "
"Loadings above 0.708 indicate that the construct explains more than 50%% of "
"the indicator's variance."
msgstr ""

msgid "Regression Coefficients"
msgstr "迴歸係數"

msgid ""
"Inner model path coefficients between constructs. The f² effect size "
"indicates the substantive impact of removing each predictor: 0.02 (small), "
"0.15 (medium), 0.35 (large)."
msgstr ""

msgid "Outcome"
msgstr "結果"

msgid ""
"Total effects combining direct and all indirect paths between constructs."
msgstr ""

msgid "Residual Correlations"
msgstr "殘差相關"

msgid ""
"Residual correlations between indicators after accounting for the construct "
"model. These represent correlated measurement errors between indicator pairs."
msgstr ""

